    "rationale": "12 of 13 V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted based on regulatory precedent for single-condition ASTM F1717 submissions and the conservative nature of the standard test configuration. Overall Medium assurance level is appropriate for a Class II device with Medium model influence and Medium decision consequence. The central credibility claim is considered supported by the ensemble of simulation and experimental evidence documented in this package.",
